Msn/Skype: Deadlyhorror (skype)

Why should I consider you: I have about 5 years experience coding and hosting and can do pretty much anything needed.
Anything else?: wont work with someone who is a complete “noob” when it comes to rsps’s. Oh and has to be in my or close to my timezone, USA > CST
Skill level?: Intermediate (professional hoster)
Position: Any
What can you add to our server?: Ill do my best to do whatever you need
